column7: Still a ways to go, huh?
Dang it! I needed more berries!
Wow! You should challenge the Merra City Gym.
I'm gonna tell my big brother!
I'm actually looking back here for a Leaf Stone.
Dang! If only my Pokémon would evolve.
Shoot! If only I had a Leaf Stone.
I have no more excuses. But we’ll win next time!
Wow! I’ve never seen those Pokémon before!
Have you beaten the Merra City Gym yet?
How many badges do you have now?
Today is just not my day.
You might even be stronger than the boss!
You’re much too strong to be a normal child.
You might even be stronger than the river!
Maybe I should have climbed the tree.
You have the perseverance of a fisher!
Even in defeat,\nwe are at peace.
I must not have gotten psyched enough!
I’m glad you’re having an easier time going this way
You’re more than ready for the trek!
Wow, you’re taking this way too seriously.
Did you find a mystery?\nIs that why you’re so strong?
Ok, maybe I can’t stop you.
I’ll allow you to stick around, I guess.
Sorry, I think the smell was me.
I knew we needed more practice.
Did training in the cavern make you so strong?
Does this mean I have to climb back down?
